360 x 640 解像度 TFT 觸控螢幕，其面積由 3.5 吋降為 3.2 吋。<br />\n<br />\n另外，X6 還預裝 Ovi 商店，並支援 Come With Music 服務。Ovi 商店是 Nokia 重點打造的商店軟件，儘管目前還比不上 Apple 的 App Store，但是將來全面的 Ovi 服務，將有機會全面超越 App Store。"},{"pid":"2f1cbbd9b571523945be2036a5def772f312b883","tid":775223,"uid":34771,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f143b87860923c6214c7535286d702e14596c8f3","tid":775223,"uid":174191,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:27:18.000Z","msg":"今晚12點就正式踏入2000年，大家有咩感受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:40:49.000Z","msg":"準備屙一督跨世紀嘅尿"},{"pid":"b6f1158af7737889eb2029884fc7e9c25170a424","tid":775223,"uid":102446,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:43:22.000Z","msg":"如果20年前有連登，會有乜野熱門TOPIC?"},{"pid":"94c7ee0750cf45e5de62a842ac092ab9899c6082","tid":775223,"uid":44243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5cec4be9b371224a4a67040e9383dbbdd79328e4","tid":775223,"uid":65429,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:05:12.000Z","msg":"反四大天王？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"突發 黎明唱到走哂音 好撚難聽"},{"pid":"203596ce52ade6cbec5e3b3ef46dde26ddde55a8","tid":775223,"uid":59283,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"[長文]董建華搞到我一無所有"},{"pid":"16ac04c2feeee928de9a69aa50a1d75980e82c51","tid":775223,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"移民jj"},{"pid":"3a03f2aebf7777b12915bdc46345b5ec795dd444","tid":775223,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:48:45.000Z","msg":"KPKP"},{"pid":"203f653ff2ae68b40756545ee1d244f1ab82e544","tid":775223,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"我在二十年後還在上連登<br />\n月入八萬"},{"pid":"4f978d98d376ff67c1a6a111b282357bf422887e","tid":775223,"uid":199776,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:20:00.000Z","msg":